Actor Frederick ‘Freddie’ Leonard has advised fans to maximise their time doing things that are productive in the New Year. The award-winning film star argued unproductivity consumes more amount of time than when you’re actually doing stuffs that are productive. He further urged fans to make it a point of call to mind their business more and gossip less, so as to achieve productivity, fruitfulness and multiplication. “The same amount of time it takes to be Unproductive is the same amount of time it takes to be PRODUCTIVE (Sometimes Shorter)”, he wrote.   Mercy Eke shares messages that won her BBNaija slot     My love for giving, by fashion designer Princewill Iwueke     Yoruba actor, Tafa Oloyede, for burial Feb. 11   “In 2022, Use Your Time More CONSTRUCTIVELY & Not Destructively. - Advertisement - “Stop trying to curse men who God has Blessed, cos you can’t. There’s NOTHING YOU CAN DO ABOUT IT.. NA GOD. “Mind Your Business More and Gossip Less.. So You Can Be Productive, Fruitful and Multiply.”